parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the airbag system can lead to injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or may deploy unexpectedly.
symptoms: failure of airbags to deploy in a crash
injuries or fatalities due to airbag malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure to complete recall repairs in a timely manner can lead to continued risk of airbag system failure, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Delayed or unavailable recall repair parts
lack of communication from dealerships or manufacturers regarding recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion or damage to the vehicle frame and structural components can lead to loss of vehicle control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: Rust or corrosion on the vehicle frame

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience sudden loss of control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: causing the check engine light to come on
or the loss of power while driving. The airbag light may also come on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to malfunction or not deploy in the event of a crash, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: indicating a problem with the airbag system. The airbag may not deploy in the event of a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch system can cause the vehicle to lose power or experience sudden loss of control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
or the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system or other components can cause a fire, which can lead to serious injury or death.
symptoms: Smoke or flames are seen coming from under the hood
or a burning smell is noticed while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and deterioration of the frame can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, leading to safety risks and potential accidents.
The cracking of the dashboard can lead to sharp debris flying in the cabin in the event of an airbag deployment, causing injury to occupants.
symptoms: particularly around the airbag and instrument panel

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to become stranded, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
The failure of the door lock actuator can cause inconvenience and safety risks, particularly if the door cannot be unlocked from the outside.
